videos.headline: Trick play leads to turnover  for San Jose State
videos.description: San Jose State WR JaQuan Blackwell is intercepted by Jaron Bryant while attempting a double pass in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Rivers evades the defense for TD
videos.description: Ronnie Rivers escapes the defense for a 15-yard touchdown run for the games first points.

videos.headline: Love picked off by Bulldog defense
videos.description: San Jose State's Josh Love is intercepted by Juju Hughes in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Rivers scores 2nd TD of quarter
videos.description: Fresno State's Ronnie Rivers pushes his way into the end zone scoring his second touchdown of the first quarter.

videos.headline: Hokit dives over defense for TD
videos.description: Fresno State's Josh Hokit gets airborne for the touchdown putting the Bulldogs up big.

videos.headline: Love connects with Oliver for TD
videos.description: San Jose State quarterback Josh Love finds Josh Oliver to avoid the shutout in the third quarter.
